HVY KL-TShM'a LKV LMYM V'aShUr 'aYN-LV KSPh LKV ShBUrV V'aKLV VLKV ShBUrV BLV'a-KSPh VBLV'a MChYUr YYN VChLB.
LMH ThShQLV-KSPh BLV'a-LChM VYGY'yKM BLV'a LShB'yH ShM'yV ShMV'y 'aLY V'aKLV- TVB VThTh'yNG BDShN NPhShKM.
HTV 'aZNKM VLKV 'aLY ShM'yV VThChY NPhShKM V'aKUrThH LKM BUrYTh 'yVLM ChSDY DVD HN'aMNYM.
HN 'yD L'aVMYM NThThYV NGYD VMTShVH L'aMYM.
HN GVY L'a-ThD'y ThQUr'a VGVY L'a-YD'yVK 'aLYK YUrVTShV LM'yN YHVH 'aLHYK VLQDVSh YShUr'aL KY Ph'aUrK.
DUrShV YHVH BHMTSh'aV QUr'aHV BHYVThV QUrVB.
Y'yZB UrSh'y DUrKV V'aYSh 'aVN MChShBThYV VYShB 'aL-YHVH VYUrChMHV V'aL- 'aLHYNV KY-YUrBH LSLVCh.
KY L'a MChShBVThY MChShBVThYKM VL'a DUrKYKM DUrKY N'aM YHVH.
KY-GBHV ShMYM M'aUrTSh KN GBHV DUrKY MDUrKYKM VMChShBThY MMChShBThYKM.
KY K'aShUr YUrD HGShM VHShLG MN-HShMYM VShMH L'a YShVB KY 'aM-HUrVH 'aTh- H'aUrTSh VHVLYDH VHTShMYChH VNThN ZUr'y LZUr'y VLChM L'aKL.
KN YHYH DBUrY 'aShUr YTSh'a MPhY L'a-YShVB 'aLY UrYQM KY 'aM-'yShH 'aTh-'aShUr ChPhTShThY VHTShLYCh 'aShUr ShLChThYV.
